---
description: When and how to use badges to convey information
globs: **/*.html
alwaysApply: true
---

 - Badges should be used to convey traits of an item, such as event.
 - Badges must always be placed immediately below the header, never anywhere else.
 - Badges go under the date and time subheader of an event.
 - Badge colors must be light blue. Do not use other badge colors.
